<p>COMPETITOR</p>
<p>aemulus refers to someone inferior who has amibitions to supass his superior.</p>
<p>certator and concertator refer to someone who is on a par with the person he or she competes with. </p>
<p>rivalitas refers to the constellation where there is competition for public estimation.</p></note></bibl>
